<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
     width="800" height="340"
     viewBox="0 0 800 340">

  <style>
    <![CDATA[
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Bravura';
      src: url('/fonts/Bravura.woff2') format('woff2'),
           url('/fonts/Bravura.woff') format('woff');
      font-weight: normal;
      font-style: normal;
    }

    .canvas-content {
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-note {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: deepskyblue;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: deepskyblue;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .char.cursor {
      fill: white;
      stroke: black;
      stroke-width: 2px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    /* Semantic element styles */
    .note-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #1e90ff;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .rest-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #808080;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .barline-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #8b008b;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .dash-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #4682b4;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .breath-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #ff6347;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .lyrics-char {
      font-size: 18px;
      fill: #666666;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .text-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #333333;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .unknown-char {
      font-size: 18px;
      fill: #999999;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }


    .octave-dot {
      fill: #ff0000;
    }

    .canvas-octave-upper {
      font-size: 12px;
      fill: red;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-octave-lower {
      font-size: 12px;
      fill: red;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-barline {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: mediumorchid;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    /* Cursor CSS removed - handled by client-side JavaScript */

    .canvas-beat-arc {
      stroke: orange;
      stroke-width: 2;
      fill: none;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .canvas-selection {
      fill: rgba(65, 105, 225, 0.4);
      stroke: none;
    }

    .line-hitbox.highlighted {
        fill: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .canvas-placeholder {
      font-size: 18px;
      fill: gray;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-unknown {
      font-size: 16px;
      fill: gray;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-title {
      font-size: 30px;
      fill: black;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-lyrics {
      font-size: 18px;
      fill: #666;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-text {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #333;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 50% { opacity: 1; }
      51%, 100% { opacity: 0; }
    }

    /* Character replacement styles removed - handled in rendering logic */
    ]]>
  </style>
  <rect width="800" height="340" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#dddddd" stroke-width="1"/>
  <g class="canvas-content" transform="translate(20, 20)">
<g class="content-line">
    <rect class="line-hitbox" x="-20" y="-20" width="800" height="60" fill="transparent" />
</g>
  </g>
  <metadata id="coordinate-data">
    <![CDATA[
    {
      "elements": [
      ],
      "characterPositions": {
        "0": {"x": 0.0, "y": 20.0},
        "1": {"x": 5.6, "y": 20.0}
      }
    }
    ]]>
  </metadata>
</svg>
